{"tid":1839560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本檢獲確診新型肺炎武漢遊客 患者赴日上飛機前已發燒","createTime":"2020-01-24T13:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T13:50:30.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0b724cfd33fb8203235bcacf788bac690bdaed20","tid":1839560,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.setn.com/m/ampnews.aspx%3fNewsID=678074\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fampnews.aspx%253fNewsID%3D678074&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77S8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=a25a067d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.setn.com/m/ampnews.aspx%3fNewsID=678074</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 即時 熱門 娛樂 影音 政治 社會 生活 地方 汽車 直播 運動 國際 財經 直播 科技 新奇 寵物 圖輯 專題<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎／日本第2例！患者是「武漢遊客」 出國前已發燒<br />\n2020/01/24 08:05<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n「2019新型冠狀病毒」（2019-nCoV）引發的「武漢肺炎」持續延燒，全球有超過600人確診武漢肺炎，其中18人死亡。日本在今（24）日出現第二起武漢肺炎確診病例，患者是一名到東京觀光的武漢遊客。<br />\n<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀&hellip;.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▲武漢肺炎持續延燒。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n根據日媒報導，患者是一名居住在武漢的40多歲男子，他在1月14日就開始發燒，15日及17日曾看過醫生，不過當時沒有診斷出武漢肺炎，個案也沒有被跟進。<br />\n<br />\n後來，男子在1月19日到日本旅行，20日曾經在當地看醫生，也沒有被診斷出武漢肺炎。不過到了22日，他發燒和喉痛仍未改善，再去看醫生時被認為是感染肺炎的徵狀，於是被送入醫院，到24日凌晨確診患上武漢肺炎，目前在東京的醫療機關住院治療。<br />\n<br />\n此外，日本上一個確診病例的，是一名居住在神奈川縣的30多歲中國籍男性，在6日從武漢返抵日本，10日患病住院，並在檢查中證實罹患新型肺炎，不過該患者在15日已康復出院。（蔣季容報導）"},{"pid":"0a06bc60c19de9c2081474fcd78490e8e53fc5fa","tid":1839560,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"快啲死撚左佢啦支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e780385f38a83e7b5d9bfebdd130fbe066c4864","tid":1839560,"uid":195540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:09:58.000Z","msg":"好快香港就會淪陷 <br />\n好似武漢咁<br />\n時間問題"},{"pid":"7d992b704c016f21fc969a738cf5e1b479d3f0c9","tid":1839560,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"聽朝早搭國泰CX450嘅人小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1839587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1839587</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac6876b0fab78a51a0643426a99eb4ac3409d027","tid":1839560,"uid":286309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:33:43.000Z","msg":"架飛機有機會有病毒<br />\n聽朝早搭國泰CX450嘅人小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1839587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1839587</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b9cdd54f5c0e4521eb4a90c7357748648e9e44bb","tid":1839560,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127e0bd82514665d00bb2e36f00cd7f251a86965","tid":1839560,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:50:30.000Z","msg":"要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77S8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=a275e059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a><br />\n要求香港真雙普選作為第二階段中美貿易協議一部份<br />\n<br />\n而家美帝要求強国簽左第二階段先撤關稅<br />\n所以強国一定要被迫情況下同美帝簽協議<br />\n香港要搭順風車<br />\n0<br />\n0"}]}